# NeuralEarn UI Design System 2026

## Philosophy

**"Minimalist, Ultra-Rounded, and butter smooth."**

Tất cả UI phải mang lại cảm giác cực kỳ tối giản, bo tròn mềm mại và cao cấp.

---

## Color System

### Primary Palette: Emerald Monochromatic

```css
/* Primary - Emerald */
.emerald-50  { color: #ecfdf5; }
.emerald-100 { color: #d1fae5; }
.emerald-200 { color: #a7f3d0; }
.emerald-300 { color: #6ee7b7; }
.emerald-400 { color: #34d399; }
.emerald-500 { color: #10b981; }  /* MAIN ACCENT */
.emerald-600 { color: #059669; }
.emerald-700 { color: #047857; }
.emerald-800 { color: #065f46; }
.emerald-900 { color: #064e3b; }
```

### Semantic Colors

| Name | Hex | Usage |
|------|-----|-------|
| Success | `#10b981` | Confirmations, positive actions |
| Warning | `#f59e0b` | Cautions, pending states |
| Error | `#ef4444` | Errors, destructive actions |
| Info | `#3b82f6` | Information, links |

### Background System

```css
/* Mobile App - Ambient Mesh Glow */
.mesh-gradient {
  background: linear-gradient(
    135deg,
    rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15) 0%,
    rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 50%,
    rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08) 100%
  );
}

/* Glassmorphism */
.glass {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

.dark .glass {
  background: rgba(24, 24, 27, 0.4);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
}
```

