## Border Radii (Ultra-Rounded)

### The Golden Rule

> **Cards: `48px` | Buttons: `full` | Inputs: `full` | Modals: `28px`**

```css
/* Card - Ultra Rounded (MANDATORY) */
.card-ultra {
  border-radius: 48px;
}

/* Buttons - Pill Shape */
.button-pill {
  border-radius: 9999px;
}

/* Small Elements - Full Round */
.icon-container {
  border-radius: 50%;
}

/* Inputs - Pill */
.input-pill {
  border-radius: 9999px;
}

/* Modals */
.modal {
  border-radius: 28px;
}

/* Tables - Medium */
.table-cell {
  border-radius: 12px;
}
```

### Anti-patterns to Avoid

```css
/* ❌ WRONG - Never use these */
border-radius: 4px;   /* Too sharp */
border-radius: 8px;   /* Still sharp */
border-radius: 16px;  /* Acceptable but not premium */

/* ✅ CORRECT - Ultra rounded */
border-radius: 48px;  /* Cards */
border-radius: 9999px; /* Buttons, Inputs, Pills */
```

